Package model.objective

package model.objective
  • Class
    Description
    ArtifactObjective
    objective based on the number of artifacts present on the placementArea, if tris = 0 then artifact variable value will contain the artifact type to count, else artifact should be null (and should be ignored), we should count the repetitions of 3 artifacts
    DiagonalShapeObjective
    objective in a diagonal shape composed of three cards identified by their relative coordinates referred to the one on the right
    ElementObjective
    objective based on the number of elements of the tipe @element present on the placementArea
    LShapeObjective
    objective in L shape composed of three cards identified by their relative coordinates referred to the card standing alone
    Objective
    inteface used for the objectives strategy pattern: identifies the right way to count points
    Shape
    shape has relative coordinates (coordinate (0,0) is omitted) to a precise card of the pattern, it will be given as parameter to the method of the placement area searching for specific patterns
